===Pronunciation===
su·per
*(General): so͞o'pə(r), /ˈsuːpə(r)/, /"su:p@(r)/
*{{UK}}: /'sju:p@/
*{{US}}: /ˈsupɚ/, /"sup@`/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-uːpə(r)|Rhymes: -uːpə(r)]]
SOO-per or SU-per

===Adjective=== 
'''super'''

#better than average, better than usual
#[[wonderful]]

